{
  "text": "ManC14 was synthesized according to a modification of a published method. [CITATION_1] D-(+)-Mannose (0.75g, 4.16mmol) was reacted with 1-tetradecanol (10.71g, 0.05mol) in 1,4-dioxane (15ml) containing 96% H 2 SO 4 (40\u00b5l) for 12h followed by neutralization and evaporation of volatile compounds. The crude product was purified by column chromatography on SiO 2 (20% EtOH/EtOAc) to obtain the product as a while power. [CITATION_2] ",
  "citation_candidates": [
